## 1. Purpose

This guide provides instructions for securely decommissioning {{ product_name }} in accordance with CRA Annex I, Part I, Section 13 requirements for secure data deletion.

## 2. Before Decommissioning

- Ensure all critical data has been exported or backed up
- Revoke any API keys, tokens, or credentials associated with this product
- Notify relevant stakeholders of the planned decommissioning

