## 4. Secure Disposal

- Remove all network connections before disposal
- Follow local regulations for electronic waste disposal
- Consider using certified e-waste recycling services

## 5. Post-Decommissioning

- Deregister the product from any cloud services
- Remove the product from any monitoring or management systems
- Update asset inventory records

---
*This guide addresses CRA Annex I, Part I, Section 13: "enable users to securely and easily remove on a permanent basis all data and settings."*
